You'll need to apply these patches manually, there's no automated
script. Go to each project dir in the AOSP tree and patch -p1 <
xxx.patch

You'll also need the wifi AWEXT driver patch from 
http://blog.linuxconsulting.ro/2010/04/porting-wifi-drivers-to-android.html

(direct link http://www.linuxconsulting.ro/android/patches/android_wext_emulation_driver_awext.patch )

